comments.comment: There was a bit of a debate on 'the other social network' to whether this means you force push, pull before you push or my suggestion that you push to a /new/ branch. XD; Always work your story on a git branch. No merge conflicts until merge.; Yeah so you would have your local branch set to push to a branch of the same name on your own private upstream (eg. on GitHub) so there are no conflicts.
